# Heavy / Dell-origin assets are intentionally NOT part of the Pages bundle.
# The Pages copy is media-light: full-res photos, videos, the pmtiles base map,
# and the full-resolution GPX stay on the Dell (served from puppyride.vinnycapp.com)
# and are fetched cross-origin at runtime. Never copy these in here — they blow up
# the deploy and defeat the point of the failover.
*.pmtiles
photos/full/
videos/
data/route.full.gpx
data/route.gpx
data/route.light.gpx
data/route.oldlongisland.gpx
data/*.test-data.json

# local/editor cruft
*.backup-*
.DS_Store
node_modules/
